      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Consumer Credit Protection Act to prevent credit card issuers from taking unfair advantage of full-time, traditional-aged, college students, to protect parents of traditional college student credit card holders, and for other purposes.</title>
